data.description:
Don't miss you chance to see this beautiful home located in Temple in Belton ISD with a community pool. This home is in the Windmill Farms community close to local shopping and dining.
This home is spacious 3 bedroom 2 1/2 Bath with office/ flex room. 
Downstairs you will find an office/ flex room, large living room, half bath, kitchen, and laundry room. On the upper level you will see the primary bedroom and bathroom, 2 additional bedrooms, an additional full bath, as well as another living area. The Primary/ Master bedroom features entry to the balcony, walk-in closet, and an oversized bathroom. Double vanities, Garden Tub, and Shower.
